    • toString

      public String toString()
      Returns the human-readable string representation of the laptop.

      The format of the string to return is: 

       Laptop ('owner') - 'age'
      • 'owner' is this laptop's owner.
      • 'age' is this laptop's title.

      For example: 

       Laptop (Thomas) - 2
